{"tid":1753037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"親共議員何君堯大敗 微博小粉紅震驚“跳腳”","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d445c2aa221a16168a74b536452c04a3715c381c","tid":1753037,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:07:09.000Z","msg":"在香港區議會選舉中，被指與7.21白衣人持械襲擊案相關，長期對抗&ldquo;反送中&rdquo;運動的親共建制派議員何君堯連任失敗。週一（11月25日）凌晨，何君堯在臉書宣佈敗選，承認輸給民主黨議員盧俊宇近1200票。該消息在大陸微博親共&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;羣體引起軒然大波。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯發文說，&ldquo;我在今次的區議會選舉中落敗，只得二千六百一十三票！雖然比上屆增加了五百多六百票，但仍輸給對手盧俊宇近一千二百票！&rdquo;，他稱，&ldquo;今年非常，選舉非常，結果也異常&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日，香港民衆在晚間遊行結束後在元朗遭到有組織的持械白衣人襲擊，45人遭打傷，1人重傷，孕婦行人也遭毆打。當晚何君堯被拍到與打人的元朗白衣人親切握手問候，被指與當地&ldquo;鄉黑&rdquo;勾結。在此後，何君堯多次公開對抗香港&ldquo;反送中&rdquo;運動人士，引起香港民衆憤慨，自7.21事件後，他的辦公服務機構多次被砸被燒。<br />\n<br />\n在何君堯敗選後，大量港人歡呼慶賀，更有人開香檳慶祝。在敗局已定後，何君堯的競選團隊黯然離去。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯敗選的消息在大陸關注香港遊行的&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;羣體中引發軒然大波，由於陸媒長期正面報道建制議員何君堯的事蹟，他的敗選令許多&ldquo;小粉紅&rdquo;表示震驚。<br />\n<br />\n香港青年論壇連登網友發現，在何君堯敗選後，有大陸&ldquo;粉紅&rdquo;在微博發帖稱，&ldquo;我真的哭了&rdquo;，&ldquo;心臟受不了了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n也有大陸網友表示，尷尬，央視還天天報道說要遵從民意，現在&ldquo;百分之80的人投票支持暴徒&rdquo;，&ldquo;中央臉肯定掛不住&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n10月29日，由於何君堯長期參與抹黑香港&ldquo;反送中&rdquo;遊行的活動，英國安格利亞魯斯金大學取消了收於他的榮譽博士學位。<br />\n<br />\n9月中旬，在何君堯發起&ldquo;全港清潔日&rdquo;，在各區清拆連儂牆後，民衆在元朗朗屏站行人天橋張貼了大量何君堯的圖像。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/316214?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F316214%3Flang%3Db5&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM29870t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=acc5ec9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/316214?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"229c79cf8706bc457300bee6c7418bc70970cd46","tid":1753037,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"為左下屆立法會，請各區議員設選民登記站，記住多一個真係好撚多<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752925</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8b8ce598f2befb7be9fa348258ce065527f44229","tid":1753037,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"齊鼓掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歌聲放 今晚開心唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請鼓掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c246ed2ff62b2fc056d84f520b449743c2c2a7e9","tid":1753037,"uid":186997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EbTQ8U1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEbTQ8U1.jpg&h=72c0b4d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06eb0c32e9e49c0e86b206f503a653e149185425","tid":1753037,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:19:36.000Z","msg":"link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c08ba8e8b963a31b0d8a6efd3e3da650f08fd9","tid":1753037,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2019-11/ry7n8eg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2019-11%2Fry7n8eg.png&h=d96a6a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2019-11/k1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2019-11%2Fk1.png&h=48bd3ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2019-11/k2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2019-11%2Fk2.png&h=c6323a3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56990204c2e47451d4e296f0f45dcab33898dde9","tid":1753037,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"何6C輸左唔緊要<br />\n我哋選村長村支書記贏番就得啦"}]}